<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_4228"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4228-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4228">National Service or the Draft for 2 years?&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8499-4049">engi0001</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">14 hours ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Its the responsibility of citizenship in exchange for the fortune of being an American. Americans should be given an opportunity to know and serve their country for two years. It would solve so much. Social and racial issuses and put the young that have no path or goals in life on the right path for a better and brighter tommorrow. Go to this link to learn more about this its a great artical from Time magazine http://www.time.com/time/specials/2007/0,28757,1657256,00.html</div>
