<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_3477"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3477-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3477">Training material YouTube&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6386-4049">Jon Galt</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Require all training materials created using federal taxpayer money be posted on a free easily accessible system such as YouTube. This will allow for reduced duplication of effort spent creating the same material in multiple locations. Also, provide a financial reward for the most viewed training material to reward high quality material creation/sharing.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3477" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3477', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2252&topicID=3477')">Comments (6)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3477"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2252">Training and Development</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=training">training</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=youtube">youtube</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=reward">reward</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3477"></div>
</div></td>
